  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its size, design, bulk, and siting, would result in an obtrusive and incompatible form of development that would fail to respect the character and appearance of the subject property and the terrace of which it forms part, contrary to policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of LP33 Hackney Local Plan (2020), and policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach), and D4 (Delivering good design), of the London Plan (2021) and the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-d6ca89c5-7fff-9db7-fc8b-bd38051b830f&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "The proposed development, by reason of its size, massing, and location, and due to the lack of supporting information such as a sunlight and daylight assessment, would have an overbearing impact on the adjoining occupiers to the east and affect daylight to 2 windows. The proposal is, therefore, contrary to policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&nbsp;"
  ],
